### Make a Transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 10,
    "description": "Test transfer",
    "recipient_phone": "123654789",
    "country_code": "CM",
    "payment_method": "Orange Money",
    "add_supplement": false
}

