### Failed Transfer (Insufficient Balance)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 999999,
    "description": "Test transfer with insufficient balance",
    "recipient_phone": "123654789",
    "country_code": "CM",
    "payment_method": "Orange Money",
    "add_supplement": false
}

### Response example for failed transfer:
# {
#     "success": false,
#     "message": "Insufficient balance",
#     "data": null
# }

### Failed Transfer (Invalid Recipient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

